Anda akan bertanggungjawab memandu.

00:32:16.480 --> 00:32:17.860
Jika kau rasa bersalah padaku,

00:32:19.270 --> 00:32:19.980
mungkin terlalu berat,

00:32:20.400 --> 00:32:21.290
hanya

00:32:21.510 --> 00:32:23.220
hulurkan bantuan.

